ZH: 我们全家每年都会去参加当地的嘉年华活动。
EN: My whole family goes to the local carnival every year.

ZH: 学校组织了一个嘉年华庆祝学期结束。
EN: The school organized a carnival to celebrate the end of the semester.

ZH: 嘉年华上有很多不同的游戏和表演。
EN: There are many different games and performances at the carnival.

ZH: 我们买了些糖果和棉花糖在嘉年华上。
EN: We bought some candy and cotton candy at the carnival.

ZH: 学校举办了一个慈善嘉年华募款给需要帮助的人们。
EN: The school hosted a charity carnival to raise money for people in need.

ZH: 嘉年华上有摩天轮，云霄飞车等很多刺激的游乐设施。
EN: The carnival has many thrilling rides like ferris wheels and roller coasters.

ZH: 我们的城市在夏天举办了一个大型嘉年华。
EN: Our city hosts a large carnival in the summer.

ZH: 孩子们喜欢在嘉年华上玩弹跳屋和射击游戏。
EN: Kids enjoy playing in bounce houses and shooting games at the carnival.

ZH: 她的生日派对是在当地的嘉年华游乐园。
EN: Her birthday party is at the local carnival amusement park.

ZH: 昨天我去参加了一个街头嘉年华。
EN: Yesterday, I went to a street carnival.

ZH: 他们在嘉年华上拍了很多照片留作纪念。
EN: They took a lot of photos at the carnival as keepsakes.

ZH: 嘉年华上有许多美食摊位，我们尝了很多不同的食物。
EN: There are many food stalls at the carnival, and we tried a lot of different foods.

ZH: 听说那个嘉年华上有一场惊险的魔术表演。
EN: I heard that there is a thrilling magic show at that carnival.

ZH: 嘉年华上的烟火表演非常炫目，让人难忘。
EN: The firework display at the carnival is dazzling and unforgettable.

ZH: 我们一群朋友组队去参加了街边嘉年华。
EN: Our group of friends went to the street carnival together.

ZH: 这个嘉年华上有很多有趣的游戏和活动。
EN: There are many fun games and activities at this carnival.

ZH: 她的公司每年都会组织一个员工家庭嘉年华。
EN: Her company organizes an employee family carnival every year.

ZH: 我在嘉年华上赢得了一个大玩具熊。
EN: I won a big stuffed bear at the carnival.

ZH: 我们在嘉年华上体验了很多刺激的过山车。
EN: We experienced many thrilling roller coasters at the carnival.

ZH: 谁想要一起去参加欢乐的嘉年华？
EN: Who wants to come with me to the fun carnival?
